<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Successful</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #27ae60;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .info-box p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #3498db;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .btn-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn-link:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
        <h1>Registration Successful!</h1>
        <p>Your account has been created successfully.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <p><span class="info-label">User ID:</span> <span class="info-value"><%= user_id %></span></p>
            <p><span class="info-label">Role:</span> <span class="info-value"><%= role %></span></p>
            <p><span class="info-label">Status:</span> <span class="info-value">Active</span></p>
        </div>

        <p>You can now login with your User ID and password.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">Please keep your credentials secure and do not share them with anyone.</p>

        <a href="/login" class="btn-link">Proceed to Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
